data.description: IMMACULATE like new home in Middleburg, with incredible amenities. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath beauty offers an open concept, making the home feel bright and airy. Featuring a large island for food prep and gatherings, plus a sizeable pantry & a huge living room to gather in. The split floor plan is perfect for families. Glass sliders and windows let in a ton of light, and you will love the huge fenced backyard with separate shed. Besides the huge slide and community pool, Azalea Ridge also offers playgrounds, soccer field, and a clubhouse with a gym. Close to shopping, dining, hospitals, and within commuting distance for the Navy Base. This home is just waiting for you and your family!
